{"title":"Chumba USA Fundraising Give-Away for Bikepacking Roots’ BIPOC Adventure Grant","link":"https://theradavist.com/bikepacking-roots-bipoc-adventure-grant/","date":1724948870000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-1.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-1.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/search/chumba/\" target=\"_blank\">Chumba USA</a> and Astral Cycling have teamed up and kitted-out a one-of-a-kind USA-built gravel adventure bike to raise funds for Bikepacking Roots’ (BPR) BIPOC Bike Adventure Grant! The Terlingua Steel frame will include Astral Outback Wheels and components from other Bikepacking Roots Sponsors White Industries, Shimano, Old Man Mountain and Paul Components. Find out how <a href=\"https://bikepackingroots.org/chumba-bike-giveaway-2024/\" target=\"_blank\">you can win it</a> below!</em><span></span></p>\n<p><em>The <a href=\"https://bikepackingroots.org/the-bipoc-bike-adventure-grant/\" target=\"_blank\">BIPOC Bike Adventure Grant Program</a> changes lives and builds community by increasing access and promoting inclusion in bikepacking and adventure cycling. Who among us hasn’t had their lives changed, grown, been empowered and healed through the power of self-propelled adventure on two wheels? This program seeks to extend that experience into those communities that have historically lacked access to the heart-filling magic of exploring the world on two wheels. The BPR’s grant program raises funds and then disperses grants to BIPOC Community Leaders committed to hosting trips, developing gear libraries, building community and spreading the love through bikepacking in their regions.</em></p>\n<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-5.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-5.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-5.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-5.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-5.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img width=\"1334\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-9.jpg?fit=1200,2000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-9.jpg?w=1334&amp;quality=75 1334w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-9.jpg?resize=1200,1799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-9.jpg?resize=768,1151&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-9.jpg?resize=1025,1536&amp;quality=75 1025w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-6-1.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-6-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-6-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-6-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-6-1.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>By donating now, you can help support inclusion in the bikepacking and cycling community AND earn a chance to win this amazing bike! The complete custom build has an Approximate Retail Value of $6,800 and includes the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span><a href=\"https://chumbausa.com/terlingua-700c-650bplus-steel\"><span>Chumba USA</span></a></span><span> Terlingua Steel Frame</span></li>\n<li><span><a href=\"https://astralcycling.com/\"><span>Astral</span></a></span><span> 700c Outback Wheels</span></li>\n<li><span><a href=\"https://bike.shimano.com/en-US/product/component/grx.html\"><span>Shimano</span></a></span><span> GRX kit</span></li>\n<li><span><a href=\"https://www.whiteind.com/\"><span>White Industries</span></a></span><span> hubs, headset and crankset</span></li>\n<li><span><a href=\"https://www.paulcomp.com/\"><span>Paul Components</span></a></span><span> bits to round it out</span></li>\n<li><span>An <a href=\"https://oldmanmountain.com/\"><span>Old Man Mountain</span></a> Elkhorn Rack</span></li>\n<li><span>Custom Bags from <a href=\"https://dispersed.bike/\"><span>Dispersed Bikepacking</span></a></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-7.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-7.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-7.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-7.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-7.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-4-1.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-4-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-4-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-4-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-4-1.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-2.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-2.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>This bike was displayed at Astral Cycling’s booth at the MADE Bike Show in Portland, Oregon from August 23-25th and will also be featured in Chumba’s booth at The Masterbuilder Bike Show in Bentonville Arkansas on September 13th-14th, but you do not need to be present to win.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-8.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-8.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-8.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-8.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Bikepacking-Roots-Fundraiser-Chumba-8.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bikepackingroots.org/chumba-bike-giveaway-2024/\" target=\"_blank\">By hitting this link</a>, you can make a donation of your selected level and enter the drawing.</p>\n<p><em>Don’t ride a 56cm frame? Not to worry – the amazing folks at Chumba will ensure you get a build with all of these great components in your size! The more you donate, the more chances you will have to win! Make a difference, have some fun, and enjoy the ride!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/bikepacking-roots-bipoc-adventure-grant/\">Chumba USA Fundraising Give-Away for Bikepacking Roots’ BIPOC Adventure Grant</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"5195b26c7a11f358887b815ab164c4f4d830a64361ff5e7041ccca7e197db9ff","category":"Cycling"}